  "detailed_description": "<br>The Bastonnes is an action / strategy game taking place in a 30’s mafia style with cartoon characters<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You have four members in your family, each has his own ability. Choose wisely your action to take advantage on your opponents<br></li><li> You may need help? Some briefcases will give you special card, it may turn the tide!<br></li><li> A unique turn based game combining strategy, action and sacrifice <br></li><li> Combat in a multiplayer, local or online, game up to 4 players or AI<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/f84ca8e505d6e8ee4ad72477102198e3.poster.avif?t=1687352669\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/f84ca8e505d6e8ee4ad72477102198e3.webm?t=1687352669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/f84ca8e505d6e8ee4ad72477102198e3.mp4?t=1687352669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple game modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Survivor Mode (standard): All actions are executed simultaneously<br></li><li> Realtime Mode: You plan one action and it's executed immediately<br></li><li> Godfather Mode: Godfather's rifles will shoot you!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Custom Settings</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Compose your team: Choose which characters will defend your colors!<br></li><li>Big Team: Five members in each families<br></li><li>Seat assignation: You can choose random or ordered assignations<br></li><li>Custom drop: You can choose turn's drop for specials and dynamites</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/cf58b39777bfa014c845d07b550b105e.poster.avif?t=1687352669\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/cf58b39777bfa014c845d07b550b105e.webm?t=1687352669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/cf58b39777bfa014c845d07b550b105e.mp4?t=1687352669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<br>The Bastonnes is an action / strategy game taking place in a 30’s mafia style with cartoon characters<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You have four members in your family, each has his own ability. Choose wisely your action to take advantage on your opponents<br></li><li> You may need help? Some briefcases will give you special card, it may turn the tide!<br></li><li> A unique turn based game combining strategy, action and sacrifice <br></li><li> Combat in a multiplayer, local or online, game up to 4 players or AI<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/f84ca8e505d6e8ee4ad72477102198e3.poster.avif?t=1687352669\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/f84ca8e505d6e8ee4ad72477102198e3.webm?t=1687352669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/f84ca8e505d6e8ee4ad72477102198e3.mp4?t=1687352669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple game modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Survivor Mode (standard): All actions are executed simultaneously<br></li><li> Realtime Mode: You plan one action and it's executed immediately<br></li><li> Godfather Mode: Godfather's rifles will shoot you!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Custom Settings</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Compose your team: Choose which characters will defend your colors!<br></li><li>Big Team: Five members in each families<br></li><li>Seat assignation: You can choose random or ordered assignations<br></li><li>Custom drop: You can choose turn's drop for specials and dynamites</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1988020/extras/cf58b39777bfa